(128, 8, 'EX', '<b>DMV Hearing</b><br/><br/>You have a right to fight your license suspension. To do this you must request a DMV hearing within 10 days of your arrest. A DUI attorney will file this request for you and represent you in the process. ', 'DMV5', 4, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
