(147, 8, 'EX', '<b>Minor Passenger</b><br/><br/>You may face additional penalties for a DUI with a passenger under the age of 18. For a first offense&#44; add at least $1000 and 100 hours of community service. For a second offense&#44; add at least $2500 and between 1 and 6 months of jail time. For a third offense&#44; add between 6 month and 2 years of jail time.', 'Minor', 28, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
