(2311, 70, 'EX', '<b>Landlord Obligations</b><br/><br/>Your landlord has up to 21 days from the day you move out to give you your full deposit back or an statement describing any deductions and the remaining deposit. If you don&#39;t get anything within 21 days&#44; you have a right to fight for your full security deposit.', '21No', 4, 'Continue,ItemYes,', '', 0),
