(2468, 73, 'EX', 'Your worker might be an <b>employee</b>&#44; since he or she is not licensed. If this becomes an issue&#44; you can present other evidence to prove that the person is actually an independent contractor.', 'Licensed', 4, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
