(2523, 74, 'ZZ', 'You are probably not an intern because you did not satisfy one or more of the factors to be classified as an unpaid intern. You may be owed wages from your employer for the work you did. A lawyer can help you recover the money you deserve. The following facts disqualify you from being an intern:<br/><br/>\n<div>{purpose}</div>\n<div>{same}<div/>\n<div>{close}<div/>\n<div>{benefit}<div/>\n<div>{job}<div/>\n<div>{paid}<div/>\n<div>{educational}<div/>', 'Intern6', 14, '0,,,', '', 0),
