(2531, 23, 'ZZ', 'If you didn&#39;t see any explanations&#44; then you probably have a decent case to obtain custody of your child. If you had negative factors affecting your case&#44; you can still argue that you deserve custody of your child. In both instances a lawyer can help you obtain custody of your child. ', '', 29, '0', '', 0),
(2533, 75, 'ZZ', 'If you did not see any recommendations&#44; your worker is probably an intern. However&#44; some states have stricter regulations in determining intern status. If you did see recommendations&#44; your worker may want to modify your internship program or you may owe wages. A lawyer can help you figure out the best way to keep your company compliant with all federal and state regulations. Failing to do so may lead to law suits and fines. ', '', 15, '0,,,', '', 0),
