(2536, 77, 'EX', '<b>NDA</b><br/><br/>You might need a Non&ndash;disclosure agreement. A Non&ndash;disclosure agreement (NDA) is an agreement between two parties that outlines confidential information that cannot be shared or disclosed to others. It is necessary if a company is sharing confidential information to another person&#44; such as an employee&#44; and wants that person not to disclose the information to others.', 'NDA', 2, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
