(2539, 77, 'MB', 'Do you hire people that produce creative or inventive work for you&#44; such as developers and designers?', '', 5, 'Yes,IP,,|No,,,', '', 0),
(2540, 77, 'EX', '<b>IP Assignment</b><br/><br/>You might need an Intellectual Property Assignment. When an employee or contractor produces work&#44; he or she holds the intellectual property rights to the work. However&#44; an IP Agreement transfers those rights to the company&#44; thereby allowing the company to use the work in whichever way it pleases.', 'IP', 6, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
