(2559, 78, 'ZZ', 'You need to be considered an &quot;Employee&quot; in order to be eligible for workers&#39; compensation. If you are unsure whether or not you are an employee or independent contractor&#44; try our guide called &quot;Am I an Independent Contractors?&quot; An attorney can also help you figure our your status. ', 'ICEE', 17, '0,,,', '', 0),
(2560, 78, 'ZZ', 'Based on your answers&#44; it is unclear whether or not you are eligible for Workers&#39; Compensation. Generally&#44; in order to be eligible you must have suffered a work-related injury. However&#44; there are numerous exceptions and&#44; depending on the specific facts of your case&#44; you may be eligible. An attorney can help you figure this out. ', 'Unclear', 18, '0,,,', '', 0),
