(2563, 76, 'EX', '<b>Incorporation</b><br/><br/>If you business is planning to grant stock options or other equity compensation&#44; you may want to think about incorporating soon. It will be easier to grant these forms of compensation via a corporation.', 'Options', 2, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
(2564, 76, 'EX', '<b>Incorporation</b><br/><br/>If you business is at a high risk of getting sued&#44; it&#39;s a good idea to incorporate soon. By forming a corporation you will be protected from personal liability. This means if you business gets sued&#44; you are not personally liable and none of your assets will be touched.', 'Sued', 4, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
(2565, 76, 'EX', '<b>Incorporate</b><br/><br/>If you are seeking venture or seed funding&#44; it&#39;s a good idea to incorporate because you will need an entity to accept the investments. In fact&#44; most VCs will not fund you unless you are incorporated. ', 'Venture', 6, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
(2566, 76, 'EX', '<b>Incorporate</b><br/><br/>If you have more than 1 founder&#44; it&#39;s a good idea to incorporate to solidify any promises and understanding on paper. During incorporation&#44; the obligations and rights of each founder will be outlined. More importantly&#44; the percentage of shares each person owns will be decided. It is easier to formalize these agreements in writing earlier than trying to clean up misunderstandings later. ', 'Founder', 8, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
(2567, 76, 'EX', '<b>Incorporate</b><br/><br/>If you plan on hiring employees or contractors&#44; it&#39;s a good idea to incorporate so the corporation is liable to these workers and not you. Furthermore&#44; you want to make sure any work produced by them is transferred to the company&#44; thereby avoiding any intellectual property disputes. This is especially important if you plan on hiring designers or developers because you want to make sure the company owns all work or code that is produced.', 'Hiring', 10, 'Continue,,,', '', 0),
(2568, 76, 'ZZ', 'Generally&#44; it might be a good idea to incorporate if your business is at risk of getting sued&#44; other people are contributing their ip&#44; you have more than 1 founder&#44; or you plan on distibuting stock to employees or investors. If you do think it&#39;s time for your business to incorporate&#44; you might want to speak with a lawyer to help you file the paperwork. Alternatively&#44; an online legal document provider might be a good option if you incorporation is fairly straightforward and you&#39;re on a budget. ', '', 11, '0', '', 0),
(2569, 2, 'ZZ', 'Now that you&#39;ve learned more about LLCs and Corporations&#44; you might be ready to form an entity for your business. A lawyer can help you file the appropriate paper work. Alternatively&#44; you could use a online document service if your formation is fairly straightforward and you&#39;re on a budget. ', '', 12, '0,,,', '', 0),
(2570, 77, 'ZZ', 'Now you have a better idea of what documents your startup may need. A lawyer can help you write these contracts. Alternatively&#44; you could use online legal document providers if you need basic documents and you&#39;re on a budget. Lastly&#44; you can choose to write your own contract&#44; but as always&#44; it&#39;s best to at least have a lawyer review them for accuracy. ', '', 7, '0,,,', '', 0),
